com.siperian.sif.message.metadata

Class MetaDataQueryGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.metadata.MetaDataBase
      • com.siperian.sif.message.metadata.MetaDataQueryGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable

    public class MetaDataQueryGroup
extends MetaDataBase
    Represents properties of a query group from the Siperian repository. A query group is a collection of MetaDataQuery objects.
    See Also:
    MetaDataQuery, DescribeSiperianObjectRequest, Serialized Form
